OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will stay dry with
OL,6,Fsunny spells, the best of these over
OL,7,FOrkney with a bit more by way of cloud
OL,8,Fover Shetland. A moderate southeast
OL,9,Fwind.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening but with a freshening
OL,13,Fsoutheast wind. Staying dry for
OL,14,FShetland overnight, but clouding over
OL,15,Fwith the odd spot of rain possible for
OL,16,FOrkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
