OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FMostly dry to start but
OL,6,Fcloud and rain will soon push north
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. Staying cloudy
OL,8,Fwith outbreaks of rain and strong
OL,9,Fsoutheast winds throughout the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FBright spells and scattered showers
OL,13,Fduring Thursday. A dry start Friday
OL,14,Fwith rain pushing northeast later.
OL,15,FShowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
